## Fork Attribution Block Template

```groovy
/**
 *  <Driver Name> (Hubitat) — Local-test fork
 *
 *  Fork by: Mads Kristensen — <YYYY-MM-DD>
 *  Source: github.com/<owner>/<repo>/blob/main/<file>
 *  Forked TEMPORARILY because: <one-line reason — list bugs>
 *  Goal: TEST FIXES LOCALLY, then submit as PR back to <owner>/<repo>.
 *        This fork should NOT outlive upstream PR acceptance — delete from this
 *        repo and switch back to upstream once merged.
 *
 *  Version: 0.1.0 — <YYYY-MM-DD> — Initial test fork; apply <audit> fixes
 *
 *  [original <author> copyright block preserved verbatim below]
 */
```

